{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Static typing（静的型付け）","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Glossary/Static_typing","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>静的型付け</strong>言語（例えば、Java, C, または C++ ）とは、コンパイル時に変数の型がわかる言語です。静的型付け言語の多くは、プログラマが明示的に型を指定しなければなりませんが、OCamlのように型推論によってプログラマが変数の型を指定しなくてもよい場合もあります。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"learn_more","title":"詳細はこちら","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"general_knowledge","title":"一般的な知識","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a title=\"Type system\" href=\"https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/Type_system\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Type system</a> on Wikipedia</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"詳細はこちら","id":"learn_more"}],"summary":"静的型付け言語（例えば、Java, C, または C++ ）とは、コンパイル時に変数の型がわかる言語です。静的型付け言語の多くは、プログラマが明示的に型を指定しなければなりませんが、OCamlのように型推論によってプログラマが変数の型を指定しなくてもよい場合もあります。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Static typing","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Tipificación estática","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Typage statique","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Статическая типизация","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/glossary/static_typing","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/glossary/static_typing/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary","title":"MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary/Static_typing","title":"Static typing（静的型付け）"}],"pageTitle":"Static typing（静的型付け） - MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}